#+TITLE:               OpenFOAM Third-Party packages 1.6
#+AUTHOR:                      OpenCFD Ltd.
#+DATE:                        November 2009
#+LINK:                  http://www.opencfd.co.uk
#+OPTIONS: author:nil ^:{}

* Description
  Scripts for building third-party packages.

* The approximate order of execution:
  + makeGcc
  + Allwmake
  + makeQt (optional)
  + makeParaView or makeParaView-python

** Optional
   + AllwmakeLibccmio
   + DistClean

* Versions and locations for the third party packages used

** Compiler
   + gcc   http://gcc.gnu.org/releases.html
   + gmp   http://gmplib.org/
           ftp://ftp.gnu.org/gnu/gmp/gmp-4.2.4.tar.bz2
   + mpfr  http://www.mpfr.org/
           http://www.mpfr.org/mpfr-current/mpfr-2.4.1.tar.bz2

** Parallel Processing
   + openmpi     http://www.open-mpi.org/software/ompi/v1.3/downloads/openmpi-1.3.4.tar.bz2
   + scotch      http://gforge.inria.fr/frs/download.php/22247/scotch_5.1.6.tar.gz

*** Still supported, but to be dropped in future versions
    + metis       http://glaros.dtc.umn.edu/gkhome/fetch/sw/metis/metis-5.0pre2.tar.gz
    + ParMetis    http://glaros.dtc.umn.edu/gkhome/fetch/sw/parmetis/ParMetis-3.1.tar.gz
    + ParMGridGen http://www-users.cs.umn.edu/~moulitsa/download/ParMGridGen-1.0.tar.gz
    + mpich       ftp://ftp.mcs.anl.gov/pub/mpi/old/mpich-1.2.4.tar.gz

** Allocation
   + hoard       http://www.cs.umass.edu/%7Eemery/hoard/hoard-3.7.1/hoard-371.tar.gz
   + fbsdmalloc  http://www.freebsd.org/cgi/cvsweb.cgi/~checkout~/src/lib/libc/stdlib/malloc.c?rev=1.43

** Misc
   + cmake       http://www.cmake.org/files/v2.6/cmake-2.6.4.tar.gz
   + Qt          http://www.qtsoftware.com/products
                 ftp://ftp.qtsoftware.com/qt/source/qt-x11-opensource-src-4.3.5.tar.bz2
   + paraview    http://www.paraview.org/files/v3.6/paraview-3.6.1.tar.gz
   + libccmio    https://wci.llnl.gov/codes/visit/3rd_party/libccmio-2.6.1.tar.gz
   + zlib        http://www.zlib.net/zlib-1.2.3.tar.gz
   + tecio       http://www.tecplot.com

